    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love making baked pasta too, *any* time of year. My favorite version has a layer of grilled eggplant inbetween the pasta layers. </></>But here&#8217;s an even more important tip: if you preheat &#038; grease the oven dish with olive oil before putting in the first layer of pasta, you&#8217;ll have a nice crunchy and chewy layer of pasta *on the underside* of your food as well! Double pleasure!</p>
