      <p>Hi Molly!  I&#39;m thinking of having the MHS tweaked tomato sauce at a dinner far away from our home and am wondering if it could be made ahead of time.  Do you think this would be alright chilled &#038; then re-heated a few days later?  Thanks so much.  (BTW, I bought veggies next to Brandon at the BFmkt a few weeks ago and was star-struck, not able to even say hi and that I appreciated Delancey and your blog so much.  I&#39;d probably drool with my jaw hanging down if I ran into you.  You&#39;re Food Stars in my book.)</p>
