      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-10874" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/06/49-degrees/#comment-10874"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-11-19T22:48:47-05:00">Saturday, November 19, 2011 at 10:48 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Kathleen, I&#39;m sorry for not replying sooner!  This may be too late, but: yes, absolutely, you can make this a few days ahead.  No problem at all!  And how fun that you ran into Brandon.  We&#39;re usually at the market every Sunday, picking up stuff for Delancey and home.  Next time, please say hi!</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
